216
00:11:19,668 --> 00:11:21,928
Why did you turn her down?

217
00:11:22,998 --> 00:11:24,568
She's the daughter of the second wife.

218
00:11:25,838 --> 00:11:28,708
His first wife passed away, and he remarried.

219
00:11:29,678 --> 00:11:31,778
Besides, Director Park has been married before.

220
00:11:32,278 --> 00:11:35,508
I'd rank her higher than these other girls.

221
00:11:36,648 --> 00:11:38,818
She was his illegitimate daughter...

222
00:11:38,818 --> 00:11:40,748
until the first wife's accidental death.

223
00:11:40,888 --> 00:11:42,588
But still, it's Haena Group.

224
00:11:48,188 --> 00:11:49,228
Never mind.

225
00:11:51,298 --> 00:11:52,898
And as for my son...

226
00:11:53,428 --> 00:11:55,498
This is technically his first marriage.

227
00:11:57,098 --> 00:11:59,608
He was just duped by a gold digger.

228
00:12:00,638 --> 00:12:02,468
Gosh, it's so upsetting to even think about.

229
